                                    "type": "text",
                                    "content": "characterizing a more precise detection overall. Conversely, the YOLOV5- X model was able to detect the largest number of BMSB reaching the highest recall. Despite achieving particularly notable metrics scores in the ONLY set, the model has depicted the least robustness against background- only patches, namely, in the ALL set. So, YOLOV5- X was prone to recognize "
